{"tid":992451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長腿正妹美到帥　騎重機環遊世界...挑戰印度「野蠻之路」","createTime":"2019-01-23T07:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T13:10:15.000Z","uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5df8ab90f93e8dd48433c1bd64e77ef8d4326b78","tid":992451,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3854/d3854254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3854%2Fd3854254.jpg&h=ad8af5df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泰國正妹娜蘇里亞汪不僅長相性感，還車技了得經常騎行世界各地。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／Ying Dusita Nasuriyawong）<br />\n實習記者陳妙津／綜合報導<br />\n泰國正妹娜蘇里亞汪（Dusita Nasuriyawong）因為火辣身材、天使臉孔，在網路上擁有高人氣。特別的是，她還是位重機好手，曾騎著重機環遊世界，還挑戰過印度拉達克，該地是世上最崎嶇的山地之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/49898562_2467585309924539_6594168962924150784_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg5-1.fna&amp;oh=98402fb3a405593c569de3eb3c48aa87&amp;oe=5CFFA27C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F49898562_2467585309924539_6594168962924150784_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg5-1.fna%26oh%3D98402fb3a405593c569de3eb3c48aa87%26oe%3D5CFFA27C&h=b751c422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/50012351_2467572459925824_6057684348872687616_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg5-1.fna&amp;oh=229940e0421303cb9b59040b410b6d7d&amp;oe=5CC9DD6F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F50012351_2467572459925824_6057684348872687616_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg5-1.fna%26oh%3D229940e0421303cb9b59040b410b6d7d%26oe%3D5CC9DD6F&h=33552ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲&nbsp;娜蘇里亞汪熱愛在網路上分享騎重機的經驗。<br />\n綜合泰媒報導，娜蘇里亞汪車技了得，曾參加2015年南非「GS TROPHY 2015」女子資格挑戰賽，2016年時則曾參與一場鐵人三項比賽，在「普吉-清邁1天1600公里」的項目中獲得第8名佳績。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/44863301_2343183625698042_6391733633706622976_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg5-1.fna&amp;oh=78ceb0e0199af2b820211fbf2bd25c65&amp;oe=5CFFCDE8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F44863301_2343183625698042_6391733633706622976_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg5-1.fna%26oh%3D78ceb0e0199af2b820211fbf2bd25c65%26oe%3D5CFFCDE8&h=a55c1df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/48392713_2428268817189522_122016284257812480_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg5-1.fna&amp;oh=52d95cd5f8bb7161f20d62566af8f22b&amp;oe=5D012410\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F48392713_2428268817189522_122016284257812480_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg5-1.fna%26oh%3D52d95cd5f8bb7161f20d62566af8f22b%26oe%3D5D012410&h=a0140a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她騎重機已經有6年時間，在任何條件的道路上都能得心應手，駕馭自如，並熱愛旅行，經常在國內外騎重機遊覽各地風景。2016年末，還去了有「野蠻之路」稱號的印度拉達克騎行，即使曾經摔傷，仍不改她征服荒路的野心，不僅拍下許多優美風景，還來回騎了2次。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3854/d3854245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3854%2Fd3854245.jpg&h=765be102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲娜蘇里亞汪征服被稱為「野蠻之路」的印度拉達克山區。<br />\n娜蘇里亞汪表示，自己的夢想就是騎著心愛重機體驗世界各地，領略人文美景，並把自己的故事寫下鼓勵更多人。目前她正騎車環遊全泰國，目前已到達曼谷，下一步計畫則是騎到印度去。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190123/1363426.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190123%2F1363426.htm&d=IoclT1kYyzcwpF8g0EMZp%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7917d50b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190123/1363426.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4d8e25bd6b4911969f28d2f54ab208ec1f2aad6a","tid":992451,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"下一步計畫則是騎到印度去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /